``I have a secret message for you,
O king.''

The king said,
``Keep silence!''

All who stood by him left him.

# Judges 03:20
Ehud came to him;
and he was sitting by himself alone in the cool upper room.

Ehud said,
``I have a message from God to you.''

He arose out of his seat.

# Judges 03:21
Ehud put out his left hand,
and took the sword from his right thigh,
and thrust it into his body.

# Judges 03:22
The handle also went in after the blade;
